page.title: 02MY DAY
page.content: Wednesday July 3rd 1985 Holly Hobby rings out 6.30 Urgh! Wednesday! Science, French, worse, Third Year Assembly! Rejoin "Swallows and Amazons".Help! 7.00, where are my socks, where's my hairbrush? "Come on Mommy,do my hair." The bell always rings before I rinse my teeth. "Morning Danielle". "Yes I've got my swimming kit, bye". Scramble,shove,third row back from the driver in the old tin can. Deathly hush,"Goodmorning,we'll sing hymn 14". Division,multiplication,ring that bell someone!Cheese sandwiches!"Bonjour Monsieur Ewers"."Yes Mr Snell I'm on the microscope"."Hallo Mom"."What's for supper"."Practice,Iknow,I'll get my guitar now"."Not 8.30 already".Swallows and Amazons afloat again.9.00 two school days to go.
